Before final code, check:

[ ] null data
[ ] empty array
[ ] invalid input
[ ] long text
[ ] very small screen
[ ] slow request
[ ] failed request
[ ] double click / repeated submit
[ ] unauthorized user
[ ] expired session
[ ] missing env var
[ ] unexpected API response

If one edge case is likely, handle it.


